<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-5523] Prevent repair among the nodes of different version</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5523</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since streaming file to the node of different version is not allowed, and in fact it would be the cause of repair hang, there is no point to allow repairing among the nodes of different versions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12645323">CASSANDRA-5523</key>
            <summary>Prevent repair among the nodes of different version</summary>
